OL,4,Celements of trans hate in Brianna's
OL,5,Cdeath'
OL,7,F"I think it was quite obvious seeing
OL,8,Fthe sequence of events and the
OL,9,Fevidence that was there was shown in
OL,10,Fcourt that... from Eddie's side, there
OL,11,Fwas elements of trans hate," Esther
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"I think he is a hateful boy, and I
OL,15,Fthink that he would probably find hate
