OL,8,Fhad an easier life and she might have
OL,9,Fnot struggled so much with anxiety and
OL,10,Fwith her mental health.
OL,12,F"If there was if mindfulness was in
OL,13,Fplace in primary school and and she
OL,14,Fhad been taught to have that mental
OL,15,Fresilience and to to develop some self-
OL,16,Fcompassion.
