OL,7,F"I just think that (life) would have
OL,8,Fbeen easier and that she would have
OL,9,Fbeen happier, she would have been able
OL,10,Fto cope better with with situations
OL,11,Fhappier.
OL,13,F"I'd like to see mindfulness embedded
OL,14,Finto every school in England."
